ote><br />\n<br />\n你所謂嘅成層，亦即係所有行有共識做同一邊，市場由佢地主導，原理都係一樣，你可以唔叫佢地係大戶，都係一個名方便理解而已"},{"pid":"a12de2a4df2ad14f4cb534e89a564ba42f5ba708","tid":162891,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>師兄有冇咩書可以打好個底？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想學VSA，睇呢本，不過佢裡面有D野同我嘅睇法唔同，佢比較複雜化，但了解概念上幾有用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tradeguider.com/mtm_251058.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tradeguider.com%2Fmtm_251058.pdf&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=04998ef3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tradeguider.com/mtm_251058.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThank you<br />\n<br />\n睇緊本書<br />\n<br />\n都係你講得正D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6c1a45daa7c3b532960009464c8e92429fffd1","tid":162891,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>師兄有冇咩書可以打好個底？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想學VSA，睇呢本，不過佢裡面有D野同我嘅睇法唔同，佢比較複雜化，但了解概念上幾有用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tradeguider.com/mtm_251058.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tradeguider.com%2Fmtm_251058.pdf&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=04998ef3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tradeguider.com/mtm_251058.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThank you<br />\n<br />\n睇緊本書<br />\n<br />\n都係你講得正D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n客氣客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fe5cd73f982276ee1b91e499c9558451cc83ca","tid":162891,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成交量冇意思<br />\n外匯冇所謂大户<br />\n一有風成層trading做同一邊<br />\n重點係個風<br />\n<br />\n俾一萬億你你都唔會夾到倉<br />\n外匯唔係恒指</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你所謂嘅成層，亦即係所有行有共識做同一邊，市場由佢地主導，原理都係一樣，你可以唔叫佢地係大戶，都係一個名方便理解而已</blockquote><br />\n重點係個風<br />\n你見人跑先跑<br />\n但其實人地係聽到槍聲就跑<br />\n已經慢左<br />\n<br />\n加上大市況前通常有好多front runner <br />\n但佢地又未必岩<br />\n如果錯就跟住輸"},{"pid":"1cd73bd8a8da1a2ee853aa66d36fab16d5a7b7ea","tid":162891,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成交量冇意思<br />\n外匯冇所謂大户<br />\n一有風成層trading做同一邊<br />\n重點係個風<br />\n<br />\n俾一萬億你你都唔會夾到倉<br />\n外匯唔係恒指</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你所謂嘅成層，亦即係所有行有共識做同一邊，市場由佢地主導，原理都係一樣，你可以唔叫佢地係大戶，都係一個名方便理解而已</blockquote><br />\n重點係個風<br />\n你見人跑先跑<br />\n但其實人地係聽到槍聲就跑<br />\n已經慢左<br />\n<br />\n加上大市況前通常有好多front runner <br />\n但佢地又未必岩<br />\n如果錯就跟住輸</blockquote><br />\n咁你有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165d0da99cf88c5e94ad80267524cf835b5c84aa","tid":162891,"uid":51724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩網的realtime fx圖有volume睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npush<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}